        ::
          schematic.q.card
    ==
  ::  ford response (time assumes nothing blocked)
  ::
  =^  results4  http-server-gate
    %-  http-server-take  :*
      http-server-gate
      now=~1111.1.3
      scry=scry-provides-code
      ^=  take-args
        :*  wire=/run-build  duct=~[/http-blah]
            ^-  (hypo sign:http-server-gate)
            :-  *type
